Class DefaultSubQueueSelection<K,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.internet2.middleware.grouper.pspng.lbmq.DefaultSubQueueSelection<K,E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LinkedBlockingMultiQueue.SubQueueSelection<K,E>

    public class DefaultSubQueueSelection<K,E>
extends Object
implements LinkedBlockingMultiQueue.SubQueueSelection<K,E>
    Chooses the next queue to be used from the highest priority priority group. If no queue is found it searches the lower priority groups and so on until it finds a queue.
